Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
get_visible_bumps(25.10)                              get_visible_bumps(25.10)

Name
       get_visible_bumps  -  Returns  all  visible bump cells in the design if
       some bumps have been hidden in the design

Syntax
       get_visible_bumps

       [-help]

       Returns all visible bump cells in the design if some  bumps  have  been
       hidden in the design.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes type and default infor-
              mation for each get_visible_bumps parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man get_visible_bumps

Examples
              * The following command returns the name of all visible bumps in
                the designs:

                innovus 17> get_visible_bumps

Related Information
              * set_visible_bumps

